title: Puppy vs pumpkin who will win?
text:
This is just too cute for words.
Just when you think pumpkin passion has permeated the populace, a puppy puts the puny pumpkin in its place.
A corgi pup has no idea what to make of a tiny pumpkin, so it does what any puppy would, tries to play with it.
Too bad the pumpkin just sits there.
